@iz3_legend wrote:

You are importing files that aren’t there. Try checking the locations of the files and then comparing it to the packaging because the compiler is telling you the files you are importing aren’t in the location you are attempting to import them from. Fixing the imports would also most likely solve your other errors. I didn’t read all of the errors, but this is just my general assumption.
